		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />There are some people who want this board to remain in operation for the next few years. This means they don't want Nintendo or another video game publisher to sue its operators, Jeremy Chadwick and Joe Parsell, into oblivion. Some of Bregalad's comments come out of frustration with people who sign up on this board and immediately start talking about making flagrantly infringing copies of copyrighted works. This has happened numerous times over the past few years.
